metadata.title: Comfortable Male Dog Diapers - 50-Pack Super Absorbent Disposable Male Dog Wraps- FlashDry Gel Technology, Wetness Indicator Doggie Diapers- Leakproof Belly Wraps for Incontinence, Excitable Urination
features: ALL-TIME PROTECTION - Prevent accidents with these specialized disposable diapers for dogs when you are having trouble with a male marking his territory, dealing with incontinence, or anxious about traveling with your pet.
100% LEAKPROOF - No Leak Security leakproof barriers all around the edges of the doggy diapers ensures nothing leaks while the wrap is on even as your little guy wiggles and runs around.

COMFORTABLE WEARING – The breathable outer layer and fur-friendly fasteners are there to make sure your dog is comfortable and stays his happy, playful self when he’s wearing the disposable dog diapers.

SUPERIOR ABSORBENCY - The ultra-absorbent core turns liquid into gel as soon as it touches the pet diaper. Moisture is instantly absorbed and wicked away from your dog’s fur for comfortable, long-lasting protection.
WETNESS INDICATION - The yellow strip running through the center of the puppy diapers will turn blue when it’s time to change the wrap so you can stop guessing and avoid leakage.
description: Keep your fur-baby comfy and dry–and your mind at ease–with PitPet Super Absorbent Disposable Male Wraps. These feature Fur-Friendly Fasteners, leak-proof barriers and a super-absorbent core. The unique stretchy material is designed to stay in place no matter how much your little wiggle-worm squirms, and the wetness indicator lets you know when it's time for a change. Accidents are bound to happen, as they say, but the one-two combination of leak-proof barriers and an extra-absorbent pad help make sure your four-legged friend’s accidental piddle stays in the diaper and not on your floor or furniture.
